abstract: The justice, 86, who was treated for chills and a fever, has had a series of health scares in the past year.
snippet: The justice, 86, who was treated for chills and a fever, has had a series of health scares in the past year.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Justice Ruth Bader Ginsburg was released from the hospital on Sunday after treatment for chills and a fever, a Supreme Court spokeswoman said. “She is home and doing well,” said the spokeswoman, Kathleen Arberg.

abstract: Mr. Bloomberg brings a huge personal fortune and moderate views to an increasingly fluid race, but issues like criminal justice and his late start loom as vulnerabilities.
snippet: Mr. Bloomberg brings a huge personal fortune and moderate views to an increasingly fluid race, but issues like criminal justice and his late start loom as vulnerabilities.
lead_paragraph: Michael R. Bloomberg announced on Sunday that he would run for president in 2020, bringing his enormous wealth and eclectic political biography into the tumultuous Democratic primary and seeking to win over skeptical liberal voters by presenting himself as a multibillion-dollar threat to President Trump.

abstract: President Klaus Iohannis claimed victory as his challenger, Viorica Dancila, conceded.
snippet: President Klaus Iohannis claimed victory as his challenger, Viorica Dancila, conceded.
lead_paragraph: BUCHAREST, Romania — In late 2016, a populist political party swept to power in Romania promising generous social spending, tax cuts and a continuation of the country’s alignment with the European Union, nine years after it had joined the bloc.

abstract: Researchers are creating tools to find A.I.-generated fake videos before they become impossible to detect. Some experts fear it is a losing battle.
